// SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for the app version. Bump here only.
//
// CalVer: YYYY.M.MICRO - no zero-pad on month, MICRO resets to 0 each month.
//   2026.6.0 = first June 2026 release; 2026.6.1 = same-month hotfix.
// CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION (build number) is a monotonic YYYYMMDD stamp.
//
// Read by: both Info.plists ($(MARKETING_VERSION)) and the Makefile
// (DMG_NAME / release tag). Pulled into the build via #include in
// StreamLib.xcconfig, which the Makefile applies with -xcconfig. NOTE:
// because the build is driven by `make` (which passes -xcconfig), the
// version is NOT set in project.pbxproj - bump it HERE, build with `make`.

MARKETING_VERSION = 2026.6.30
CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION = 20260641
